import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Navbar, NavItem, Nav, NavDropdown, Form, FormControl, Button, Container, Row, InputGroup, Image, ListGroup } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { Link, NavLink } from 'react-router-dom';
import { GoSearch } from 'react-icons/go'

class Navbar_Menu extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Container fluid>
                <Container>
                    <Navbar expand="lg">
                        <Link to='/' > <Navbar.Brand>Blog Vũ</Navbar.Brand></Link>
                        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                        <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                            <Nav className="mr-auto">
                                <Nav.Link href="#home">News</Nav.Link>
                                <Nav.Link href="#link">My CV</Nav.Link>
                                <NavDropdown title="Lĩnh vực" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                                    <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Action</NavDropdown.Item>
                                    <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Another action</NavDropdown.Item>
                                    <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">Something</NavDropdown.Item>
                                    <NavDropdown.Divider />
                                    <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">Separated link</NavDropdown.Item>
                                </NavDropdown>
                            </Nav>
                            <Form inline>
                                <Form.Label htmlFor="inlineFormInputGroupUsername" srOnly>
                                    Username
      </Form.Label>
                                <InputGroup>
                                    <FormControl placeholder="Tìm kiếm" />
                                    <InputGroup.Prepend>
                                        <Button className='border' style={{ backgroundColor: '#5488c7' }}><GoSearch className='text-white'></GoSearch></Button>
                                    </InputGroup.Prepend>
                                </InputGroup>
                            </Form>

                        </Navbar.Collapse>
                        {!this.props.login ?
                            <Link to='/login'>
                                <NavItem href='/login' className='pl-1'>Login/Registor</NavItem>
                            </Link> :
                            <NavItem>Login Successful</NavItem>}
                    </Navbar>
                </Container>
                <Row>
                    <Image fluid src='https://images.viblo.asia/full/5ce3a357-fe69-4a26-8b31-be94aabbf254.png' rounded />
                </Row>

                <Row className=' d-flex flex-nowrap justify-content-around text-center' style={{ backgroundColor: '#0b1a33' }}>
                    <ListGroup horizontal variant="flush">
                        <ListGroup.Item style={{backgroundColor:'none'}}>
                            <Link className='text-white text-uppercase p-3 w-100' to='/'>Tin mới nhất</Link>
                        </ListGroup.Item>

                        <ListGroup.Item style={{backgroundColor:'none'}}>
                            <Link className='text-white text-uppercase p-3' to='/series'>Series</Link>
                        </ListGroup.Item>

                        <ListGroup.Item style={{backgroundColor:'none'}}>
                            <Link className='text-white text-uppercase p-3' to='/trending'>Trending</Link>
                        </ListGroup.Item>

                        <ListGroup.Item style={{backgroundColor:'none'}}>
                            <Link className='text-white text-uppercase p-3' to='/post'>Create Post!</Link>
                        </ListGroup.Item>
                    </ListGroup >
                </Row >
                <Container>
                    {this.props.children}
                </Container>
            </Container >

        );
    }
}

export default Navbar_Menu;
